Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.45,0:01:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第七十七話\N下關也有緋村道場\N出現另一位拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.99,0:01:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再過三天才有船去大阪\N在那之前要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.39,0:02:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離東京還很遠 慢慢走嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.43,0:02:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住宿費又要增加了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.03,0:02:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是赤間關這地方不錯啊\N特產不愧是特產
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.24,0:02:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這河豚超級好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.14,0:02:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥 你再多嚼一下再吞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.81,0:02:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀 狼吞虎嚥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.11,0:02:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小孩就是這樣\N我才討厭跟小孩在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.08,0:02:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要留下我的份哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.98,0:02:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐再來一瓶酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.42,0:02:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.52,0:02:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把盤子放下來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.92,0:02:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.02,0:02:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們倆的臉漲得像河豚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.39,0:02:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈…看起來很難吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.73,0:02:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.57,0:02:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼 混蛋\N我說把酒拿來沒聽懂嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.04,0:02:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是客人\N您再白吃白喝下去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.41,0:02:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想趕我們出去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.14,0:02:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是自由民權運動的壯士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.58,0:02:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要讓你知道\N輕視天狗黨會有何下場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.69,0:03:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到外面去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.39,0:03:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要到外面的人是你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.49,0:03:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.23,0:03:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐視這種人渣鬧事\N神谷活心流可是會名聲掃地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.56,0:03:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是什麼人\N女人跟小孩別強出頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.70,0:03:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心討皮肉痛哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.17,0:03:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡\N對你好你就爬到頭上來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.52,0:03:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管 砍啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.29,0:03:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢著！慢著慢著！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.26,0:03:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個唱戲的是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.73,0:03:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…你是拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.10,0:03:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.27,0:03:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家等你很久啦\N拔刀齊！大師！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.38,0:04:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓幕末的京都  飄下腥風血雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.48,0:04:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連新撰組都害怕的\N傳說中的斬人拔刀齊就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.36,0:04:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左手臂這十字刀疤是最佳證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.40,0:04:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有！緋村 你其實是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.53,0:04:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.70,0:04:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操你在懷疑什麼\N刀疤在這裏 這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.34,0:04:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一樣都是左邊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.81,0:04:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頭目 要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.58,0:04:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如今天下太平\N我自己封住這夢幻般的神劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.42,0:04:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.28,0:04:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是只要我拔出這把劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.45,0:04:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四周必然頓時化為血海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.86,0:04:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣你們還想逼我拔刀嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.93,0:04:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣 怎樣 怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.01,0:05:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 今天就這樣放過你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.68,0:05:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我記住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.71,0:05:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼 光會說大話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.05,0:05:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厲害 日本第一 好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.69,0:05:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.22,0:05:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必道謝\N我只是做應該做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.03,0:05:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是指那件事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.53,0:05:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過去使用殺人劍的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.47,0:05:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在為了贖罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.50,0:05:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨時隨地\N都在為眾人幸福祈禱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.41,0:05:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.28,0:05:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你問我怎麼辦\N我覺得沒什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.61,0:05:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼這樣置身事外啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.42,0:05:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是他又沒有做壞事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.35,0:05:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們看他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.59,0:05:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這樣我很困擾\N我不是為了錢而助人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.26,0:05:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 他在收錢耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.07,0:06:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣你也不在乎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.24,0:06:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 收人報酬並不算…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.18,0:06:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他打著你的名字耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.31,0:06:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…不…這…\N重要的是找今晚住的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.82,0:06:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去拆穿那傢伙的謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.95,0:06:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.92,0:06:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,京都三條河原\N響起刀劍交鋒的迴響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.13,0:06:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人是近藤勇率領的新撰組\N隨便一數 竟有一百零八人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.13,0:06:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然而我拔刀齊以一當百\N打呀打呀打呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.87,0:06:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人是十幾萬的幕府軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.21,0:06:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,島羽伏見活脫脫一副\N慘烈的地獄景像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.38,0:06:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奮勇穿梭在槍林彈雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.95,0:06:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打這個 扔那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.68,0:06:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.99,0:06:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 這邊也客滿了\N根本就沒地方住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.29,0:06:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰 剛剛我跟大家提過的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.83,0:07:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？收保鏢費？\N這樣跟地痞流氓沒兩樣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.37,0:07:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可原諒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.57,0:07:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.50,0:07:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對是吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.90,0:07:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.90,0:07:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別氣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.11,0:07:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼別氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.24,0:07:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這地方本來是長州藩地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.18,0:07:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長州系的維新志士\N沒有人不知道斬人拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.92,0:07:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利用劍心的名氣最快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.12,0:07:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我覺得他不像壞人\N應該多調查一下得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.99,0:07:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼天真話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.16,0:07:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.33,0:07:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…最重要的是找住的地方\N我從中午手就麻麻的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.77,0:07:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會是河豚中毒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.00,0:07:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 中毒了 你吃那麼多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.67,0:07:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.94,0:07:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找醫生？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.88,0:07:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對 去假拔刀齊那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.58,0:07:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.29,0:08:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是廢寺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.59,0:08:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是\N神佛分離令的時代被廢棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.80,0:08:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重要 問題是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.24,0:08:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流緋村道場？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.17,0:08:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪有人厚臉皮到這程度的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.74,0:08:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.81,0:08:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.05,0:08:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是剛才的人\N沒想到你們特地來道謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.56,0:08:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不道謝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.79,0:08:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您真愛開玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.03,0:08:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 快點說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.20,0:08:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你叫劍心啊\N找我有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.24,0:08:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃…這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.88,0:08:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在慢吞吞幹什麼 去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.78,0:09:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 你腰上那把劍…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.69,0:09:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了\N原來你也是學劍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.46,0:09:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來 原來如此\N你想在我的道場拜師啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.23,0:09:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼\N本人拔刀齊馬上給你教導
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.67,0:09:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先從架勢開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.14,0:09:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行不行 不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.48,0:09:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太不像樣了 你在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.01,0:09:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快撿起木刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.68,0:09:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃 是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.45,0:09:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.49,0:09:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍尖下垂了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.99,0:09:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抬太高 你的腰是怎麼了\N打直呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.73,0:09:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肩膀放鬆 放鬆 好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.70,0:09:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.77,0:09:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別放鬆 不準得意忘形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.30,0:09:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你這個人太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.01,0:10:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師 捨三欺負人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.31,0:10:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對 是新太先揍人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.48,0:10:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啦 你們別吵架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.58,0:10:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.75,0:10:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尿尿…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.29,0:10:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師 肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.39,0:10:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.63,0:10:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 不好意思\N這孩子拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.63,0:10:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.57,0:10:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乖乖 廁所在哪裏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.54,0:10:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等…\N這裏到底是什麼怪道場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.98,0:10:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰 孩子們的飯\N一定要弄平均
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.35,0:10:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然孩子們會吵架的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.29,0:10:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.66,0:10:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.46,0:10:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無處可住就住我家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.70,0:11:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣吧 決定了決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.17,0:11:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 恭敬不如從命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.50,0:11:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.95,0:11:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過來吧 我很強的哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.45,0:11:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就猜到你會用那招…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.16,0:11:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.20,0:11:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收穫是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.77,0:11:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於在河豚店的那些怪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.80,0:11:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是自稱天狗黨的那群人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.60,0:11:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.04,0:11:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們根本就不是什麼\N自由民權運動的壯士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.74,0:11:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是群普通的壞蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.81,0:11:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前他們在這裏是胡作非為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.45,0:11:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是自從那個\N假拔刀齊登場以後就變乖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.35,0:11:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,於是鎮上的人都很歡迎他？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.59,0:11:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他會跟人收錢耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.49,0:12:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是他收錢並沒有拿來揮霍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.97,0:12:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個老師說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.90,0:12:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些孩子全是以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.74,0:12:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在西南之役和維新的時候\N失去父母的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.11,0:12:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此\N他是為了照料孩子們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.68,0:12:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個大叔是好人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.34,0:12:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 難道要繼續\N讓拔刀齊囂張下去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.35,0:12:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 不能再讓鎮上的人\N輕視我們下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.55,0:13:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼就快點殺他吧\N我猜你們沒那個膽子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.92,0:13:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.56,0:13:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道我們是天狗黨還…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.57,0:13:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初齊十郎兵衛老師\N是來殺死拔刀齊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.71,0:13:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師在池田屋騷動的時候\N在嵐山曾看過拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.92,0:13:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 如你所說的是個\N具有豪傑風範的拿劍的大漢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.49,0:13:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個工作費用很高的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.13,0:13:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.33,0:13:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢竟要殺的是\N傳說中的斬人拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.24,0:13:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問不能再便宜一點嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.44,0:13:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼看都不像真的拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.31,0:14:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有很多小孩在發育期呀\N真的 請再算便宜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.72,0:14:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他臉上的塗鴉\N是什麼咒法呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.76,0:14:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.06,0:14:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.66,0:14:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天一定要跟你分出勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.07,0:14:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不怕死的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.24,0:14:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那張臉是怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.27,0:14:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們想逼我拔出秘劍\N飛天御劍流之劍嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.95,0:14:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師 好可怕哦 老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.65,0:14:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們退後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.98,0:14:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操 孩子們交給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.02,0:14:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.43,0:14:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 誰想先下黃泉呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.03,0:14:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.17,0:14:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來呀 來呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.54,0:15:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我當你的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.54,0:15:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我見識見識你的秘劍吧\N拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.09,0:15:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙…\N不是虛張聲勢應付得了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.63,0:15:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我認真起來是很可怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.83,0:15:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刀一拔出你就會死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.14,0:15:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不在乎嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.87,0:15:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會死的是誰 打看看才知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.48,0:15:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那男人知道他是冒牌的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.35,0:15:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要打了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.02,0:15:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.89,0:15:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在這裏別亂跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.63,0:15:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢著 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.04,0:16:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 等一下呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.81,0:16:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是…我是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.38,0:16:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是真的拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.85,0:16:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 你千真萬確是斬人拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.52,0:16:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.17,0:16:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.77,0:16:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.77,0:16:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.54,0:16:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 你覺悟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.74,0:16:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說過我不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.25,0:16:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是真是假\N對我來說都無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.42,0:16:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只想殺死傳說中的\N斬人拔刀齊來揚名立萬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.70,0:17:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你快念佛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.18,0:17:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.98,0:17:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.16,0:17:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.16,0:17:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 不可以亂來\N敵人不是你能應付的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.17,0:17:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是普通人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.18,0:17:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紅髮…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.48,0:17:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左臉頰有十字刀疤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.25,0:17:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.96,0:18:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流 龍槌閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.60,0:18:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不、不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.60,0:18:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這男人是真的拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.67,0:18:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心是…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.38,0:18:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 已經結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.41,0:18:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊先生 菜頭放哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.75,0:18:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…我…這…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.29,0:18:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是這樣呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.19,0:18:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想要他們的命就乖乖聽話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.76,0:18:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快棄刀吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.70,0:18:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師好可怕 好可怕 別亂動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.14,0:18:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師…好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.11,0:18:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新太！捨三！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.44,0:18:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢著 別衝動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.98,0:18:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.85,0:19:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准傷害那些孩子\N要殺就殺我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.22,0:19:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.47,0:19:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.77,0:19:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們倆沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.61,0:19:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.58,0:19:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 拔刀齊先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.45,0:19:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道是您本人\N真不知該如何謝罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.05,0:19:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 你不用謝罪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.92,0:19:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 那你到底是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.33,0:19:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫小川兵藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.73,0:19:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以成為劍客為志向\N出來做修行之旅的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.40,0:19:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是技術一直沒有長進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.27,0:19:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,於是利用賣蟾蜍油來餬口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.17,0:20:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些孩子是走江湖時遇見的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.24,0:20:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我沒有錢養他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.24,0:20:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正困擾時就靈光一閃\N想到利用斬人拔刀齊的傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.22,0:20:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然是賣蟾蜍油的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.95,0:20:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你的手腕才有刀疤啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.55,0:20:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 這點傷只要\N塗上蟾蜍油一下子就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.36,0:20:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這把劍沒做生意之後\N好像從沒使用過嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.63,0:20:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怪不得不能拔出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.97,0:20:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慚愧啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.40,0:20:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師為什麼道歉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.54,0:20:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來老師不是拔刀齊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.01,0:20:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 新太\N我也得向大家道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.34,0:20:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算不是拔刀齊\N老師還是很強的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.25,0:20:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你救了我們的呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.82,0:20:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師就是老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.52,0:20:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀對呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.59,0:20:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.55,0:20:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以\N以後繼續當我們的老師吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.49,0:20:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.46,0:20:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了！太棒了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.63,0:21:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊 祝你平安無事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.20,0:21:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小川\N這名字我早在十年前就拋棄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.14,0:21:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的我是緋村劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.91,0:21:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.28,0:21:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 知道那帶有\N不祥回憶的名字能助人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.78,0:21:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.95,0:21:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說\N我以後能繼續使用了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.15,0:21:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.89,0:21:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太感謝了 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.86,0:21:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來 大家也道謝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.06,0:21:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你 劍心哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.00,0:21:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,常常在呃的大哥 謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.46,0:21:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人一點也不悔改耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.03,0:21:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無藥可救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.34,0:21:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的骨氣令人欽佩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.47,0:21:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比真人更勇壯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.37,0:21:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.21,0:21:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見了！再見了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.39,0:21:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船出航了 卻沒冒煙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.89,0:22:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為帆船是不會冒煙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.19,0:22:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帆船在海上越行越遠\N海鷗也在啼叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.50,0:22:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哭著送行的女人講：
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.13,0:22:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,親愛的你好冷漠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.57,0:22:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人不可以輕易上吊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.70,0:22:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以吊著的是河豚燈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.97,0:22:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 太陽又在赤間關升起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.94,0:22:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣 緋村劍心一行人\N離開大阪出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.18,0:22:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可喜可賀 可喜可賀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.29,0:22:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.42,0:22:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 兵藏老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.89,0:22:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫我拔刀齊 拔刀齊

